data.description:
Located on a quiet cul-de-Sac  and home is on an oversized lot, which backs up to dedicated  green space. Home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with updated flooring. Has a spacious open concept , dining, kitchen and living. Primary suite has walk in closet with double sinks with views of the outdoors. Has a two car garage and large patio space for entertaining .  
Boasts energy efficient features including a tankless water heater and low average  utility costs. FLOOD ZONE X. New ROOF , old one being replaced.
